title: Paul Ducco
content:
**[Indices](http://web.archive.org/web/20130816080202/http:/typophile.com/wiki/Indices) : [Designers](http://web.archive.org/web/20130816080202/http:/typophile.com/wiki/Designers) : [Paul Ducco](http://web.archive.org/web/20130816080202/http:/www.solid-creative.com/)**

[Paul Ducco](http://web.archive.org/web/20130816080202/http:/www.allthingsconsidered.com.au/) is a multidisciplinary visual designer and typographyer based in Melbourne, [Australia](http://web.archive.org/web/20130816080202/http:/typophile.com/wiki/Australia).

Paul can be contacted for creative projects through his Melbourne based [All Things Considered](http://web.archive.org/web/20130816080202/http:/typophile.com/wiki/All%20Things%20Considered).
author: Ratbaggy
